# Security headers for static hosts that read a _headers file
# (Cloudflare Pages, Netlify). Ignored by GitHub Pages — harmless there.
# No CSP here: the in-page <meta> CSP handles that, and connect-src must stay
# open for arbitrary Plex servers.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), camera=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=()
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin-allow-popups
